<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>164</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<title>nǐ shì rén shì jiān de guāng 迦南164</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 nǐ shì rén shì jiān de guāng tiān de de zhǔ zǎi, rèn shì nǐ de nà yī tiān nán wàng jì
 wǒ yī shēng yōng yǒu nǐ kuài lè wú bǐ, yuè fú shì yuè gān tián, tián rú mì,
 zhǐ yǒu nǐ cái néng ràng wǒ huó zhe xiàng rén, zhǐ yǒu nǐ cái néng ràng wǒ rèn shì zì jǐ,
 rèn dìng nǐ shì dào lù zhēn lǐ shēng mìng tóu kào zài nǐ yǒng héng de ài lǐ
 ó zhǔ ài nǐ bù biàn, ó zhǔ zhǎo dào le nǐ
 wǒ xīn jī dòng líng huān xǐ, yōng yǒu nǐ kuài lè wú bǐ.</lyrics>
</song>